        "Description": "There has been an incident at the Gama hospital in Hokkaido, Japan. Four morticians were found dead in the hospital&apos;s basement with multiple stab wounds. There has been no solid evidence found for the case, except for one thing.\r\rThe corpse of an unnamed motorcyclist was checked in the same day but has mysteriously disappeared.",
